## Scrollbar Visibility (System Preferences > General > Show scrollbars)
## Command:
##   $ defaults write NSGlobalDomain AppleShowScrollBars -string <option>
## Where <option> can be any of the following:
## [1] "Automatic" : scrollbar appears both when you start scrolling and when the cursor is in the area of the scrollbar
## [2] "WhenScrolling" : scrollbars only show up when you start scrolling
## [3] "Always" : scrollbars will always be visible even when you are not scrolling
defaults write NSGlobalDomain AppleShowScrollBars -string "Always"
